QuestData.Title: Za'Tual
QuestData.Description: The Zandalari have been a constant nuisance since we arrived on this island. I've assigned Archmage Lan'dalock to take charge of dismantling their presence at Za'Tual, in the south.$B$BReport to him when you are best able. He will have work for you.
QuestData.LogDescription: Find Archmage Lan'dalock outside of Za'Tual.
QuestData.RewardText: One more to join the Zandalari hunt? Good. Very good.
